WEBVTT

00:00:00.682 --> 00:00:02.499
-NOSTA SHESTOVA GODA

00:00:02.657 --> 00:00:04.375
ETTA POPUGAEVA

00:00:04.378 --> 00:00:06.077
KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:12.939 --> 00:00:14.261
efsher gedenkt ir

00:00:15.414 --> 00:00:18.564
ayer, ayer tante Feyge

00:00:18.705 --> 00:00:21.537
mit GUSTAVn flegn zikh farnemen mit

00:00:21.537 --> 00:00:23.930
baytn zakhn oyf shpayz.

00:00:23.531 --> 00:00:24.352
ye.

00:00:24.965 --> 00:00:26.312
dos iz geven.

00:00:26.315 --> 00:00:28.456
zi flegt zukhn in

00:00:28.456 --> 00:00:32.554
in, avekleygn a, nemen a pekele un zi flegt ibergebn

00:00:32.728 --> 00:00:36.683
un, un zi flegt baytn oyf shpayz. dos veys ikh.

00:00:35.563 --> 00:00:37.684
vemen flegt zi ibergebn, veyst ir?

00:00:37.410 --> 00:00:42.707
GUSTAV, GUSTAV flegt kumen. az er flegt, (er hot) gehat a profesye az er zol kumen in ovnt un der

00:00:42.752 --> 00:00:43.627
flegt im

00:00:43.663 --> 00:00:47.480
un zi flegt aleyn oykhet geyn epes vu baytn ober vu veys ikh nit.

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:48.365
ober da-

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:48.636
zi flegt brengen milkh

00:00:49.130 --> 00:00:51.335
dan ven flegt zi geyn oyf der arbet.

00:00:49.140 --> 00:00:51.130
fleg zi brengen.

00:00:51.130 --> 00:00:52.000
ye.

00:00:52.067 --> 00:00:55.757
flegt zi oysbaytn gevise zakhn. ir veyst velkhe zakhn flegt men baytn?

00:00:59.711 --> 00:01:01.022
ir gedenkt nit, yo?

00:01:01.652 --> 00:01:03.688
mit dos hot zikh farnumen ayer tante.

00:01:04.554 --> 00:01:08.210
iz, azoy hot ir gelebt mit dem, mit der tante di gantse tsayt.

00:01:09.144 --> 00:01:10.168
in geto.

00:01:09.347 --> 00:01:11.980
mit der tante, ye. di gantse tsayt bin ikh geven UNK

00:01:11.675 --> 00:01:15.196
ir gedenkt in geto az s'iz forgekumen a kinder-aktsye?

00:01:15.185 --> 00:01:15.922
ye.

00:01:16.130 --> 00:01:17.559
dos gedenk ikh oykh.

00:01:17.868 --> 00:01:20.431
ven s'iz forgekumen a kinder-aktsye, oto di

00:01:20.431 --> 00:01:26.486
mayn khaverte Leyele iz umgekumen dan in der kinder-aktsye, ober ikh bin a dank got geblibn lebn.

00:01:26.238 --> 00:01:29.810
vos hot ir geton? vi (azoy) hot dos oysgezen di kinder-aktsye in ayere oygn?

00:01:31.267 --> 00:01:34.150
m'hot aroysge- tsuzamengeklibn di kinder

00:01:34.150 --> 00:01:40.189
un m'hot zey aroysgefirt oyf umbrengen (un) avekgefirt oyfn nayntn fort dakht zikh hot men zey gefirt.

00:01:40.565 --> 00:01:43.560
ober ikh bin nit geven in der UNK

00:01:42.354 --> 00:01:43.732
un vu zayt ir geven?

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:45.230
oykh geven bahaltn.

00:01:44.953 --> 00:01:47.563
in dem zelbikn, hintern almer.

00:01:45.660 --> 00:01:49.727
in dem zelbikn, ye. dem zelbn ort bin ikh geven bahaltn.

00:01:49.998 --> 00:01:53.750
nor ikh veys az es zaynen on di, ot di shkheyne

00:01:53.762 --> 00:01:56.256
meydele iz umgekumen in der aktsye.

00:01:56.256 --> 00:01:58.273
un di tante flegt mir zogn

00:01:58.273 --> 00:01:59.927
az du host

00:01:59.927 --> 00:02:02.694
a gute beterin, di mamen, derfar iz

00:02:02.694 --> 00:02:04.016
hit zi dir oys.

00:02:04.224 --> 00:02:08.117
un derfar, fun alts blaybstu lebn. got

00:02:08.223 --> 00:02:11.660
 hert, zi bet far dir di gantse tsayt.

00:02:12.358 --> 00:02:15.578
azoy gedenk ikh flegt di tante mir dertseyln,

00:02:15.578 --> 00:02:16.234
zogn.

00:02:16.863 --> 00:02:22.257
 un in tog fun der kinder-aktsye hot aykh di tante geheysn krikhn in, in, in baheltenish.

00:02:21.102 --> 00:02:25.447
in di, ye. bahelte- un zi hot mir

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:30.816
zogt mir, der baheltenisht vu ir zayt geven in tsayt fun der kinder-aktsye, andere aktsyes

00:02:30.816 --> 00:02:34.424
iz geven a groyse, a sakh mentshn zaynen geke- hobn gekent dortn araynge-

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:36.300
neyn, neyn, neyn, nit keyn sakh mentshn.

00:02:36.300 --> 00:02:39.727
me- mir zaynen mit Leyelen flegn mir arayngeyn dortn.

00:02:40.202 --> 00:02:41.395
ober in tsayt fun k-

00:02:40.691 --> 00:02:45.253
un di tante flegt aroysgeyn, veys ikh nit; zi flegt vayzt zikh oys vu

00:02:45.253 --> 00:02:46.997
zi flegt undz farshlisn

00:02:47.188 --> 00:02:51.604
un zogn oyb me vet, a shlisl hobn mir gehat fun un-, der

00:02:51.812 --> 00:02:55.791
fun der tir, un a shlisl hot gehat fun undzer tsimer GUSTAV,

00:02:55.794 --> 00:03:00.470
hot zi gezogt "ir zitst shtilerheyt, nor redt tsvishn zikh nit nor mit

00:03:00.470 --> 00:03:03.062
mit di hent," flegn mir zikh haltn tsuzamen.

00:03:04.434 --> 00:03:05.824
un azoy flegt ir

00:03:05.824 --> 00:03:08.051
ober in dem tog fun der kinder-aktsye

00:03:08.079 --> 00:03:11.415
hot Leyele nisht gegangen mit aykh in, in der bahelten-

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:14.868
neyn, zi iz nit UNK gegangen; ikh veys nit vi zi iz aroys

00:03:14.913 --> 00:03:18.820
az m'hot ir avekgesh- avekgetribn tsu der, tsu der shkhite.

00:03:18.643 --> 00:03:20.882
ir zayt dan geven aleyn in baheltenish

00:03:20.972 --> 00:03:24.848
efsher gedenkt ir umgefer, vifl tsayt zayt ir opgezesn in baheltenish?

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:30.568
a tog UNK gedenk ikh bin ikh geven gezesn.

00:03:33.172 --> 00:03:37.166
un vi azoy, vi azoy zikh tsuzamengeleygt der lebn nokh a

00:03:37.256 --> 00:03:39.478
nokh dem, nokh der kinder-aktsye?

00:03:40.057 --> 00:03:41.570
der lebn vi s'iz geven?

00:03:41.812 --> 00:03:43.545
zeyer troyerik.

00:03:44.816 --> 00:03:48.776
zeyer troyerik, vayle yeder, yeder shtub iz geven

00:03:48.900 --> 00:03:51.993
di shkheynim hobn zeyer baveynt di di kinder.

00:03:52.038 --> 00:03:56.741
un mir hobn oykhet ge(ton), di tante iz geven h-, zi flegt veynen un veynen un veynen.

00:03:57.185 --> 00:04:01.246
un ikh oykhet di gantse tsayt. zeyer ge- troyerik geven.

00:04:01.674 --> 00:04:02.529
(un)

00:04:02.670 --> 00:04:04.017
nor zi hot gezogt

00:04:04.037 --> 00:04:05.485
az

00:04:05.485 --> 00:04:06.506
"di, dir

00:04:06.506 --> 00:04:11.501
ikh hob dokh tsuzamengeredt," hot zi mir shoyn dan gezogt, "ikh hob zikh tsuzamengeredt mit GUSTAVn

00:04:11.546 --> 00:04:14.392
un er vet dir avekfirn tsu zayne bakente."

00:04:16.001 --> 00:04:19.286
ir gedenkt dem tog ven ir hot farlozn dos geto?

00:04:20.270 --> 00:04:24.435
dem tog ven s'iz geven gedenk ikh nit nor er iz gekumen in ovnt.

00:04:24.472 --> 00:04:26.089
er hot mir tsugenumen

00:04:26.089 --> 00:04:29.127
tsu zikh, hob ikh b- bay im ibergenekhtikt

00:04:29.127 --> 00:04:33.261
un oyf in der fri, zeyer

00:04:33.264 --> 00:04:34.805
fri; s'iz nokh geven

00:04:34.805 --> 00:04:37.126
vos, ah vifl azoy

00:04:37.126 --> 00:04:39.789
in nokh nit likhtik

00:04:39.845 --> 00:04:44.348
hot er farshpant a, shpa- a ferd, un mir zaynen a-

00:04:44.348 --> 00:04:45.631
avekgeforn

00:04:47.962 --> 00:04:49.326
efsher gedenkt ir

00:04:49.329 --> 00:04:52.698
vi zayt ir aroys fun geto, durkhn toyer tsu durkhn tsam?

00:04:52.595 --> 00:04:55.065
durkhn tsam zaynen mir aroys.

00:04:55.286 --> 00:04:56.394
durkhn tsam?

00:04:56.231 --> 00:04:59.860
mit im bin ikh aroys; er hot mir gefirt UNK tsam fun geto.

00:04:57.328 --> 00:04:59.314
ye, durkhn tsam fun geto?

00:05:00.416 --> 00:05:03.535
un (nakh-) az mir zaynen avekgeforn mit im

00:05:03.538 --> 00:05:06.244
(azoy) flegn mir UNK geforn a tsayt

00:05:06.272 --> 00:05:07.898
er flegt zikh opshteln

00:05:07.898 --> 00:05:10.437
merheyt flegn mir zikh opshteln in vald.

00:05:10.440 --> 00:05:13.269
er flegt gebn esn dem ferd

00:05:13.545 --> 00:05:17.542
un mir flegn opesn, un forn vayter.

00:05:17.578 --> 00:05:20.630
vifl, vifl tsayt zaynen mir geforn, nor mir

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:22.601
flegn nekhtikn oykhet

00:05:22.674 --> 00:05:27.660
in vald flegn mir nekhtikn, (bay na-) un nakher oyf morgn flegn mir vayter forn.

00:05:27.483 --> 00:05:30.346
vifl teg hot es zikh gedoyert ayer, ayer foreray?

00:05:31.196 --> 00:05:35.375
epes a fir teg zaynen mir gez- ge(UNK) geforn.

00:05:35.887 --> 00:05:38.581
nakher zaynen mir gekumen lebn Smargon

00:05:38.823 --> 00:05:42.348
in a dorf, BELAYA

00:05:42.348 --> 00:05:43.509
hot geheysn der dorf.

00:05:43.953 --> 00:05:48.110
er iz arayn mit mir tsu a ke- a

00:05:48.110 --> 00:05:50.816
(s'iz dortn alt ge-) a eltere froy geven

00:05:51.024 --> 00:05:56.520
nit gor keyn eltere, ober tsu, in mayne oygn iz zi dan geven shoyn a

00:05:57.639 --> 00:06:00.654
er hot gevelt mir iberlozn bay ir

00:06:00.778 --> 00:06:05.753
nor zi hot zikh nit ongenumen; zi zogt i- do kumen zeyer a sakh daytshn.

00:06:05.753 --> 00:06:08.146
mir vashn vesh far di daytshn

00:06:08.422 --> 00:06:11.673
un iberlozn do di kind kenen mir nit.

00:06:13.299 --> 00:06:15.080
zogt er "afil-"

00:06:15.797 --> 00:06:17.617
vosere shprakh hot zi geredt?

00:06:17.617 --> 00:06:18.441
di froy?

00:06:18.450 --> 00:06:20.753
di froy hot geredt rusish.

00:06:22.682 --> 00:06:24.088
az

00:06:24.116 --> 00:06:29.859
nakher az zi hot me- afile ibernekhtikn hot zi undz nit gekent iberlozn

00:06:29.859 --> 00:06:32.177
vayl zi zogt "do kenen kumen daytshn."

00:06:32.807 --> 00:06:38.019
zaynen, iz hot er mir avekgefirt in a tsveyte dorf; dortn geven KLIDENYATY hot (gehey-) di dorf.

00:06:38.019 --> 00:06:39.113
KLIDENYATY.

00:06:39.658 --> 00:06:42.937
dortn oykhet tsu an eltere froy mit a man

00:06:42.937 --> 00:06:44.161
nu, azoyne nit

00:06:44.161 --> 00:06:46.337
keyn alte, nor shoyn in

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:47.431
eltere

00:06:47.657 --> 00:06:48.557
mentshn.

00:06:48.557 --> 00:06:50.877
bay, mit zey hot er a tsayt geredt.

00:06:50.897 --> 00:06:56.227
nakher hot er gezogt, er hot ibergenekhtikt un oyf morgn zogt er "ikh loz dir do iber.

00:06:56.229 --> 00:06:58.400
dir vet do zayn bay zey gut"

00:06:58.963 --> 00:07:01.151
un er iz avekgeforn oyf karik.

00:07:01.562 --> 00:07:03.362
un ir zayt geblibn in KLIDENYATY.

00:07:02.422 --> 00:07:05.322
un ikh bin geblibn in KILDENYATY.

00:07:05.561 --> 00:07:09.032
zey hobn geheysn SAVITSKI di, di mishpokhe.

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:11.749
UNK a m- a man mit a froy.

00:07:11.973 --> 00:07:13.565
zey hobn gehat eygene kinder

00:07:13.565 --> 00:07:14.752
di SAVITSKIs?

00:07:14.180 --> 00:07:16.288
zey zaynen geven eltere mentshn.

00:07:16.783 --> 00:07:18.560
zey hobn gehat a tokhter.

00:07:18.588 --> 00:07:24.306
ot di tokhter hot mir gekumen un tsugenumen, in a por teg hot tsugenumen mir

00:07:24.306 --> 00:07:27.104
in a dorf PEREVES'YE hot zi gelebt.

00:07:27.212 --> 00:07:30.250
dos iz geven di SAVITSKI's tokhter.

00:07:30.637 --> 00:07:32.237
mit a man hot zi gelebt

00:07:32.274 --> 00:07:36.077
un zey hobn gehat tsvey kinder kleyne. eyne hot geheysn (STENYA).

00:07:36.088 --> 00:07:38.276
un di tsveyte Zhanet.

00:07:39.294 --> 00:07:41.634
di (STENYA) iz geven a kleyninke

00:07:41.741 --> 00:07:45.569
un mir hobn zey ge(UNK) hot genumen az ikh zol zayn bay zey a dinst

00:07:45.569 --> 00:07:46.427
tsu

00:07:46.567 --> 00:07:49.906
oyfpa- mit di kinderlekh shpiln.

00:07:49.906 --> 00:07:51.694
di kleyne iz geven a

00:07:51.694 --> 00:07:53.851
nit keyn polnem yor

00:07:53.958 --> 00:07:56.230
un di gresere iz shoyn geven dray yor.

00:07:56.540 --> 00:08:01.293
ikh fleg vign ir, gebn fun a, milkh on-

00:08:01.434 --> 00:08:02.761
onvaremen.

00:08:02.936 --> 00:08:05.580
eyn mol zaynen zey avekgeforn in gest

00:08:05.703 --> 00:08:08.785
un bay mir iz geven aza geshvir tsvishn fis.

00:08:09.281 --> 00:08:14.459
ober ikh hob gehat moyre tsu zogn di, di, di di baleboste.

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:13.730
baleboste.

00:08:14.462 --> 00:08:18.152
vayl efsher dos nem- kenen zikh onnemen fun mir.

00:08:19.423 --> 00:08:26.968
ober mir iz geven azoy shver tsu oyfshteyn, tsu, a gantse nakht hob ikh nit geshlofn; m'hot mir gerisn der

00:08:26.968 --> 00:08:27.938
geshvir.

00:08:27.287 --> 00:08:28.176
vund.

00:08:28.502 --> 00:08:30.668
un az di, di

00:08:30.668 --> 00:08:33.829
s- meydele hot geveynt un ikh hob gedarft aropgeyn

00:08:34.171 --> 00:08:35.836
onvaremen esn

00:08:36.112 --> 00:08:36.793
fleg ikh

00:08:36.793 --> 00:08:40.039
bin ikh ge(poyzet); kh'hob nit gekent shoyn zikh oys(beygn).

00:08:40.938 --> 00:08:44.420
kh'hob ongevaremt esn; kh'hob ir gegebn, un zi hot ge-

00:08:44.420 --> 00:08:47.357
un mir, ikh vig ir un mir vilt zikh shlofn

00:08:47.357 --> 00:08:48.915
un zi veynt un veynt.

00:08:49.055 --> 00:08:52.377
(ober gedenk) ikh dem fal, ikh hob ir gegebn aza treysl

00:08:52.397 --> 00:08:55.052
un zi iz zikh fargangen; zi iz gevorn bloy.

00:08:55.063 --> 00:08:58.618
hob ikh gemeynt ikh hob ir avekgeharget; kh'hob ir gekhapt oyf di hent

00:08:58.708 --> 00:09:00.333
un ikh hob genumen mit ir

00:09:00.378 --> 00:09:03.227
kushn un ikh hob ir genumen treyslen

00:09:03.264 --> 00:09:04.924
un ikh hob genumen veynen

00:09:04.935 --> 00:09:10.076
nor zi hot zikh opgekhapt; nor dan iz geven aza shrek; ikh hob gemeynt ikh hob (ir) avekgeharget.

00:09:10.335 --> 00:09:12.678
nokh dem hob ikh shoyn keyn mol

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:16.466
nit ir azoy shtark ge-

00:09:16.466 --> 00:09:19.829
getreyslt vayl ikh hob zikh d- azoy geshrokn az

00:09:20.814 --> 00:09:23.495
zi iz, zi hot nit, ikh hob a-

00:09:23.495 --> 00:09:26.660
zi iz der- dershtikt gevorn hob ikh gemeynt.

00:09:26.602 --> 00:09:29.747
 antshuldikt, di mishpokhe SAVITSKI,

00:09:29.758 --> 00:09:31.896
zey hobn gevust az ir zayt a yidishe?

00:09:32.289 --> 00:09:34.629
zey hobn mir keyn mol nit gefregt

00:09:34.702 --> 00:09:38.952
nor er az er hot mir (gebrakht) hot er mir gezogt in veg az m'iz geforn

00:09:38.952 --> 00:09:41.784
"zogt az ir zayt (SHUVALA VAZINA)

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:44.267
un zogt az ir zayt fun VELIKIE LUKI."

00:09:44.267 --> 00:09:48.247
ikh zol nit zogn az ikh bin a yidishe un keynem zol ikh nit zogn, zol ikh nit dertseyln.

00:09:49.113 --> 00:09:55.380
un di mishpokhe in PEREVES'YE vu ikh bin geven, dos iz KARTAVIK hobn zey ge- di mishpokhe geven.

00:09:55.380 --> 00:09:58.553
dos iz geven ire a tokhter, nor der man iz geven

00:09:58.553 --> 00:10:02.034
a poylisher (iz er) geven; tsvishn UNK zikh flegn zey reydn poylish.

00:10:02.664 --> 00:10:07.366
un di SAVITSKIs flegn oykh redn poylish. rusish hot nor geredt ot di in BELAYA.

00:10:08.030 --> 00:10:11.166
vos hot gelernt aykh GUSTAV tsu zogn

00:10:11.166 --> 00:10:14.217
oybe me vet aykh fregn vu zaynen ah ayere eltern?

00:10:13.683 --> 00:10:16.749
hot er mir gezogt ikh zol zogn az ikh bin fun VELIKIE LUKI

00:10:16.856 --> 00:10:20.647
un dortn zaynen umgekumen di eltern, un ikh bin zayner a fraynt.

00:10:22.627 --> 00:10:26.590
ah, in PEREVES'YE iz mir oysgekumen zeyer shver tsu arbetn.

00:10:26.590 --> 00:10:28.478
kh'hob gepashet di ki

00:10:28.652 --> 00:10:33.338
un mir flegn aroysgeyn, shoyn geven herbst iz a, der, flegt zayn der

00:10:33.427 --> 00:10:38.383
di groz shoyn mit a ROSA a kalte, mir flegn, ikh fleg geyn borves.

00:10:38.608 --> 00:10:41.218
a kleyd fleg ikh geyn a, fun a zak

00:10:41.983 --> 00:10:47.394
nor nit ale tog flegt men pashen. tsvey mol in vokh flegt undz oyskumen vayl dortn iz geven

00:10:47.450 --> 00:10:50.037
flegn geyn in der gantser dorf

00:10:50.037 --> 00:10:51.413
flegt

00:10:51.413 --> 00:10:52.288
pashen.

00:10:52.918 --> 00:10:57.907
s'flegt mir oyskumen tsu kormenen, tsu melkn di ki,

00:10:58.115 --> 00:11:03.377
di ki fun onfang hob ikh fleg ikh moyre hobn far a ku, nor nakher hob ikh zikh ayngevoynt, zey hobn mir gezogt

00:11:03.397 --> 00:11:06.918
az di ku darf zayn fun rekhtn zayt, di kop

00:11:06.975 --> 00:11:10.381
un me darf oystsien azoy fil di di di brust

00:11:09.185 --> 00:11:10.310
tsitske

00:11:10.381 --> 00:11:13.849
az s'zol zikh keyn kapl nit blaybn; anit vet iber-

00:11:13.849 --> 00:11:16.700
-brenen un s'vet zayn zeyer f-

00:11:16.728 --> 00:11:18.089
tut vey.

00:11:18.618 --> 00:11:26.040
un nakher in shtal iz geven khazeyrim; kh'hob, fleg ikh shlepn dem emer un zey gisn di, di, fleg hobn moyre

00:11:26.060 --> 00:11:29.635
far di khazeyrim, nor nakher hob ikh shoyn ayngevoynt tsu,

00:11:29.635 --> 00:11:32.889
kh'hob shoyn nit gehat moyre, nit far di ki, nit far di

00:11:33.182 --> 00:11:36.163
 nit far di behey- nit far di khazeyrim.

00:11:36.405 --> 00:11:39.870
kh'fleg in der fri, in ovnt onleygn

00:11:39.881 --> 00:11:41.878
holts in oyvn

00:11:41.878 --> 00:11:47.236
un in der fri araynkrikhn, vayl er iz geven, kh'bin geven a kleyninke

00:11:47.236 --> 00:11:50.358
un di holts, der oyvn iz geven a tifer, fleg ikh araynkrikhn

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:54.196
un nakh- nakher oyf tsurik shoyn untervarfn a shvebele.

00:11:54.196 --> 00:11:56.154
dortn geven korke mit

00:11:57.276 --> 00:11:58.559
(kedey) s'zol zikh ontsindn

00:11:58.559 --> 00:12:00.829
un fleg mit der, s'flegt dokh zayn der

00:12:00.857 --> 00:12:02.927
DYM, der

00:12:02.477 --> 00:12:03.349
roykh.

00:12:03.152 --> 00:12:04.474
roykh fleg ikh

00:12:04.474 --> 00:12:06.875
aroyskrikhn mit

00:12:07.370 --> 00:12:09.407
ZA- ZA- ZADOM.

00:12:09.564 --> 00:12:10.959
mit di hintn, ye?

00:12:09.783 --> 00:12:12.224
fun, mitn hintn fun, fun

00:12:12.298 --> 00:12:13.828
fun oyvn.

00:12:15.150 --> 00:12:20.983
esn fleg ikh zeyer veynik. kh'hob gehat, getrakht oyb ikh vel esn a sakh, hungerik fleg

00:12:21.056 --> 00:12:22.217
halb hungerik

00:12:22.237 --> 00:12:26.200
vayl oyb ikh vel esn a sakh, zey flegn zogn s'iz alts tayer, s'iz keyn zakh nito

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:27.868
veln zey mir nit haltn.

00:12:27.924 --> 00:12:29.960
nor vos, ikh fleg n- geyn

00:12:30.017 --> 00:12:32.221
melkn di ki

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.348
fleg ikh zikh ontrinken mit milkh.

00:12:35.028 --> 00:12:36.366
dos iz geven mayn

00:12:36.366 --> 00:12:38.144
OSNOVNOYE esn.

00:12:37.442 --> 00:12:39.984
hoypt-esn, hoypt- -shpayz.

00:12:38.580 --> 00:12:40.254
ye, zol ikh shoyn zayn zat.

00:12:41.947 --> 00:12:44.543
nokh va- vaser fleg ikh shlepn fun,

00:12:44.543 --> 00:12:47.108
der brunem iz geven a bisl vayt fun

00:12:47.108 --> 00:12:50.272
undzer sht- di shtub in derfl iz geshtanen

00:12:50.283 --> 00:12:51.543
di letste.

00:12:51.819 --> 00:12:56.808
un far un (dort) vu s'iz geven der brunem hot gelebt zayner a bruder

00:12:56.882 --> 00:12:58.699
METSHKE's dem balebos.

00:12:58.569 --> 00:12:59.930
dem KARTAVIK's.

00:12:58.822 --> 00:13:01.536
dem KARTAVIK, ye, dos iz geven a bruder.

00:13:01.536 --> 00:13:04.945
VOLODYA hot er geheysn, KARTAVIK oykhet, mit a froy.

00:13:04.945 --> 00:13:08.064
zi iz geven fun VARSHAVA, fun Poyln, di froy zayne.

00:13:09.285 --> 00:13:12.674
un OSOBENNO iz geven shver tsu shlepn di vaser az s'iz geven der brunem

00:13:12.693 --> 00:13:13.907
mit LYOD far...

00:13:13.689 --> 00:13:14.747
mit ayz.

00:13:14.027 --> 00:13:16.030
mit ayz far, far

00:13:15.630 --> 00:13:16.721
farfroyrn.

00:13:16.040 --> 00:13:16.788
vinter.

00:13:18.465 --> 00:13:24.891
nu, un eyn fal zeyer a, ge- gedenk ikh az, tsu im flegt kumen aza

00:13:24.891 --> 00:13:27.313
fun Smargon PENTKOVSKI, a

00:13:27.313 --> 00:13:29.225
pan mit a groysn boykh

00:13:29.450 --> 00:13:30.322
boykh.

00:13:30.817 --> 00:13:35.835
der, eyn mol hot er oyfgenumen a pekl un zogt

00:13:35.835 --> 00:13:38.569
"du vest ge-, tsugeyn in Smargon

00:13:38.597 --> 00:13:41.893
un avektrogn PENTKOVSKIn dem pekl."

00:13:41.904 --> 00:13:43.620
nit keyn groyse pekele.

00:13:44.520 --> 00:13:47.822
nor shoyn ongeshribn geven PENTKOVSKOMU

00:13:49.059 --> 00:13:50.184
oyf poylish?

00:13:49.987 --> 00:13:51.070
oyf poylish.

00:13:51.354 --> 00:13:54.639
o- (ober) er zogt "oyb er vet nit zayn in shtub

00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:59.077
zolst kumen in el- arbetn in komendantur."

00:13:59.285 --> 00:14:04.218
er hot mir gezogt vu, s'iz nit vayt fun shtub, un er hot, derts- derklert vu.

00:14:04.218 --> 00:14:07.109
zolst im avektrogn in komendatur dem pekele.

00:14:07.183 --> 00:14:10.547
ikh bin gegangen oyfn veg, un ikh hob geveynt un kh'hob ge-

00:14:10.558 --> 00:14:13.357
un ikh hob gebetn bay got er zol nor zayn in shtub.

00:14:13.357 --> 00:14:15.953
ikh zol, mir zol nit oyskumen geyn in komendatur.

00:14:16.211 --> 00:14:20.460
vayle ikh hob getrakht, alts eyns bin ikh enlekh oyf a yidishe, m'vet mir derkonen

00:14:20.463 --> 00:14:23.180
di daytshn, dan veln zey mir avekhargenen.

00:14:23.670 --> 00:14:25.363
ikh bin gekumen tsum shtub

00:14:25.363 --> 00:14:27.174
un tsum groysn

00:14:28.597 --> 00:14:30.836
(boday) iz di shtub geven farshlosn.

00:14:31.415 --> 00:14:36.108
kh'hob zikh avekgezetst, dortn iz geven a gertl. kh'hob zikh aropgezetst in gortn

00:14:36.108 --> 00:14:38.248
oyf a benkele, a (SUD).

00:14:38.958 --> 00:14:40.437
a SKAMEYKA.

00:14:40.443 --> 00:14:41.534
a benkele?

00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:42.567
un ikh, a benkl. un ikh

00:14:42.567 --> 00:14:45.871
trakht, vi zol ikh itster geyn dortn in komendantur?

00:14:46.097 --> 00:14:49.781
efsher zol ikh farlorn dem, zogn ikh hob farlorn dem pekl

00:14:49.809 --> 00:14:53.533
oder zogn az bay mir hot men opgenumen bay mir oyfn veg.

00:14:53.690 --> 00:14:56.995
ober vi ken ikh zogn a (lign dort) az es zol nit kenen

00:14:56.995 --> 00:15:00.772
(iz neyn,) ikh muz zikh tsuzamennemen mit ale

00:15:02.347 --> 00:15:03.407
koykhes

00:15:02.499 --> 00:15:03.067
yo.

00:15:03.427 --> 00:15:05.635
un geyn in komendantur.

00:15:05.672 --> 00:15:08.453
nu, un azoy bin ikh avek in komendantur, ikh ze

00:15:08.453 --> 00:15:11.471
oyfn shvel zaynen geshtanen daytshn.

00:15:11.949 --> 00:15:13.547
ikh bin tsugegangen.

00:15:13.603 --> 00:15:17.276
zog ikh "PENTKOVSKOMU. PANU PENTKOVSKOMU. PANU

00:15:17.400 --> 00:15:18.609
PENTKOVSKOMU."

00:15:18.986 --> 00:15:20.375
"DIESE, DIESE"

00:15:20.403 --> 00:15:24.721
hobn zey ongehoybn oyf daytsh, "KINDER, PENTKOWSKI, PENTKOWSKI.

00:15:24.721 --> 00:15:25.767
KOMM, HIER."

00:15:25.770 --> 00:15:29.353
ober ikh hob zikh gemakht ikh farshtey dos nisht vos zey reydn.

00:15:29.353 --> 00:15:32.914
nu, s'iz aroysgegangen PENTKOVSKI, er hot bay mir tsugenumen dem pekele

00:15:32.942 --> 00:15:36.896
ober (az) ikh hob avekge(UNK) fun ge- fun dem ort

00:15:36.907 --> 00:15:39.351
iz mir getreyslt di hent mit di fis.

00:15:39.351 --> 00:15:41.435
a tson oyf a tson hot bay mir nit,

00:15:41.435 --> 00:15:44.192
ikh hob geshpirt vi di tseyner hobn bay mir geklapt

00:15:45.007 --> 00:15:46.790
vayl,

00:15:47.184 --> 00:15:48.326
fun shrek.

00:15:48.433 --> 00:15:53.119
un nakher hob ikh dray teg gelegn krank fun, fun, fun shrek.

00:15:53.192 --> 00:15:56.477
ober ikh hob keyn zakh k- nit dertseylt; ikh hob keyn zakh nit gevizn

00:15:56.550 --> 00:16:00.409
az me zol mir, vayle dos iz geven zeyer

00:16:00.465 --> 00:16:04.290
nor in zikh hob ikh UNK mit vemen tsu der- dertseyln hob ikh dos nit gekent

00:16:05.156 --> 00:16:09.490
farshteyt zikh, di mishpokhe KARTAVIK hot nisht farshtanen vos far a gefar hot aykh gedrot in

00:16:09.527 --> 00:16:11.074
in der komendantur.

00:16:11.417 --> 00:16:15.259
un aleyn hobn zey keyn mol nisht nis- nisht gezogt az ir zayt a yidishe.

00:16:14.724 --> 00:16:18.870
keyn zakh, ober eyn mol hobn zey gezogt epes. di broyt hob ikh avekgeleygt

00:16:18.960 --> 00:16:22.113
nit oyf a, ot azoy vi mit

00:16:22.113 --> 00:16:24.011
nu, vu broyt ligt oybn

00:16:24.011 --> 00:16:25.918
di korkn untn, di vayse

00:16:25.918 --> 00:16:27.594
ober UNK oyf a

00:16:27.650 --> 00:16:29.062
oyf a farkerte zayt.

00:16:28.477 --> 00:16:29.563
oyf farkert.

00:16:29.563 --> 00:16:30.955
zogn zey "oy!

00:16:30.955 --> 00:16:34.479
P- PO ZYDEWSKU CHLEB POLOZHILA

00:16:34.265 --> 00:16:36.284
dos iz vi a yidishe, ye?

00:16:34.822 --> 00:16:37.224
UNK, ye, oyf a yid-

00:16:37.224 --> 00:16:40.132
vi a yidishe hob ikh avekgeleygt di, di, di, di broyt.

00:16:41.353 --> 00:16:42.309
un

00:16:41.505 --> 00:16:43.643
nor dos iz mir shoyn oykh geven a shrek.

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:49.920
ir gedenkt, dan di tsayt ven di rusn zaynen arayn in ayer dorf?

00:16:49.605 --> 00:16:52.502
dos gedenk ikh, az di rusn zaynen arayn

00:16:52.575 --> 00:16:56.766
der balebos hot (itst) far

00:16:56.766 --> 00:16:59.910
az ikh hob genumen a vogn mit a ferd farshpant

00:17:00.101 --> 00:17:05.259
un avekgeforn in mil, s'iz nit vayt geven a mil dortn ibern veldl.

00:17:05.601 --> 00:17:07.789
un er iz avekgeforn makhn mel.

00:17:08.639 --> 00:17:15.066
un nit keyn groyse tsayt iz avek, er iz gekumen tsurik un er zogt es s'iz ge- der front iz shoyn

00:17:15.066 --> 00:17:16.247
nit vayt

00:17:16.247 --> 00:17:20.441
un der mil-, der miler iz antlofn, er hot far-

00:17:20.441 --> 00:17:23.619
-klapt di mil, un di mil arbet shoyn nit.

00:17:24.806 --> 00:17:27.309
er hot ge- er iz gekumen un er hot gezogt

00:17:27.309 --> 00:17:28.508
dos hot er

00:17:28.508 --> 00:17:31.368
az der front, es geyen di rusishe

00:17:31.368 --> 00:17:34.790
bin ikh arayngelofn in shtal un ikh hob zikh genumen kushn mit di ki.

00:17:35.252 --> 00:17:37.322
kh'hob genumen tantsn fun freyd.

00:17:37.395 --> 00:17:42.165
vayl ikh hob getrakht efsher lebt nokh ver, di, di, mayn tante geblibn lebn.

00:17:43.385 --> 00:17:47.058
in di, di teg gedenk ikh. dem tog gedenk ikh zeyer gut.

00:17:48.774 --> 00:17:54.264
ah dos iz geven no- zey zaynen nokh nit geven di rusishe, nor mir gekumen un gezogt.

00:17:54.371 --> 00:17:58.553
nor az di rusishe, az di, di armey iz shoyn geku- -kumen

00:17:58.556 --> 00:18:01.414
iz dortn geven nit vayt fun PEREVES'YE

00:18:01.442 --> 00:18:06.127
a veldl, nokh im geven der taykh, der Nyeman fleg durkh- fleg durkhgeyn.

00:18:07.213 --> 00:18:12.230
iz m'hot zikh genumen hern vi shiseray

00:18:15.504 --> 00:18:17.344
(hot) zikh gerisn bombes

00:18:17.372 --> 00:18:20.424
un mir zaynen fun shtub, dortn iz geven a bunker aza.

00:18:20.460 --> 00:18:23.621
zaynen mir in bunker, di gantse mishpokhe zaynen

00:18:23.621 --> 00:18:27.013
di ki, mit di ferd hot men tsugebe-

00:18:27.013 --> 00:18:29.957
tsugebundn lebn bunker

00:18:29.977 --> 00:18:34.806
un dortn geven nit vayt di PEREPRAVA, s'hot di gantse tsayt gehert vi di shiserayen

00:18:34.314 --> 00:18:35.895
vos iz di PEREPRAVA?

00:18:35.214 --> 00:18:40.480
a PRAVA, dortn iz geven a brod, un dortn (do) iz durkhgegangen di armey, vi, vi, farshtey ikh.

00:18:40.480 --> 00:18:42.344
dos iz geven a PEREPRAVA vayl di r-

00:18:42.344 --> 00:18:45.204
di soldatn zaynen gegangen, ye, un zey ho-

00:18:42.347 --> 00:18:43.286
dos iz a

00:18:45.215 --> 00:18:47.217
f- durkhn taykh.

00:18:46.937 --> 00:18:50.627
dos iz a ort vu me ken zikh ariber- vu me ken aribergeyn dem taykh.

00:18:48.590 --> 00:18:51.234
ariber(UNK) dem taykh, ye.

00:18:51.695 --> 00:19:00.370
 a gantsn tog zaynen mir gezesn dortn ober, me- z- dortn f- zeyer gut geshpirt di, di klaperayen, di, fun di bombes.

00:18:59.323 --> 00:19:00.549
fun di bombes.

00:19:01.010 --> 00:19:08.424
oyf morgn in der fri hobn zey zikh, hobn zikh di gantse mishpokhe fun KARTAVIK, di shvester iz oykh geven un der

00:19:08.424 --> 00:19:09.783
un der bruder zayner,

00:19:09.783 --> 00:19:13.335
hobn mir zikh ibergeklibn, dortn iz ah oykhet a derfl, nor vayter

00:19:13.335 --> 00:19:15.579
oyf der tsveyter ve-

00:19:15.579 --> 00:19:17.205
zayt vald.

00:19:17.312 --> 00:19:20.532
dortn iz oykh geven bunkers, mistome fun yener krig.

00:19:20.532 --> 00:19:24.675
yene iz geven groyse; do iz geven a kleyner bunker, dos iz geven nor far di mishpokhe.

00:19:24.675 --> 00:19:27.350
un dortn iz shoyn geven a bunker, zaynen geven di

00:19:27.350 --> 00:19:30.430
a halber derfl, s'iz nit keyn groyser dorf geven.

00:19:30.430 --> 00:19:31.214
nor

00:19:31.214 --> 00:19:34.639
dortn oykh di (felder), UNK shoyn gebundn di kien.

00:19:34.659 --> 00:19:38.335
nor dortn zaynen durkhgeforn s- eroplanen

00:19:38.335 --> 00:19:41.144
hobn zey geshosn, (geVSTRESHCHAYET) azoy

00:19:41.144 --> 00:19:45.844
 ober zey ge- nit getrofn. nor s'flegn durkhloyfn

00:19:41.443 --> 00:19:42.568
getrofn.

00:19:45.844 --> 00:19:48.105
etlekhe mol iz geven az m'hot geshosn.

00:19:48.125 --> 00:19:49.936
nu, un nakher in a

00:19:49.936 --> 00:19:54.532
in, in ovnt shoyn in arayn, un es hobn zikh shoyn bavizn soldatn.

00:19:54.808 --> 00:19:59.505
(s'hobn) zikh bavizn soldatn, m'hot zey ongekormet, ongekormet

00:19:59.505 --> 00:20:02.261
gegebn milkh

00:20:02.334 --> 00:20:06.702
oysgetrunken, nu un nakher oyf morgn zaynen mir shoyn avek in

00:20:06.722 --> 00:20:08.990
in shtiber, in shtub.

00:20:08.983 --> 00:20:13.601
efsher gedenkt ir, vi hot zikh ongerufn di der derfele, der kleyninker derfele?

00:20:13.674 --> 00:20:16.267
ot dos i- dos iz geven PEREVES'YE.

00:20:16.138 --> 00:20:17.283
neyn, ir zogt az

00:20:16.650 --> 00:20:17.606
PEREVES'YE.

00:20:17.283 --> 00:20:21.347
un der k- derfele v- vu ir zayt gegangen aribern vald zikh bahaltn?

00:20:21.960 --> 00:20:26.274
dos iz in dem, dos iz der vald geshtanen, der dorf iz geshtanen in vald.

00:20:26.837 --> 00:20:29.813
nor dos iz geven fun eyn zayt l- neenter tsum taykh

00:20:29.813 --> 00:20:31.658
un dos iz geven fun tsveytn zayt dorf.

00:20:31.477 --> 00:20:32.551
ober der d-

00:20:31.759 --> 00:20:33.429
dos iz der zelber dorf UNK

00:20:32.709 --> 00:20:34.577
der zelber dorf PEREVES'YE.

00:20:33.590 --> 00:20:35.950
ye, ye, in vald iz do a veldl.

00:20:34.667 --> 00:20:37.935
efsher gedenkt ir, vi hot zikh ongerufn der taykh?

00:20:38.548 --> 00:20:42.401
dos iz Nyeman PO MOEMU geven. Nyeman, nit Vileyke. dos iz Nyeman.

00:20:42.446 --> 00:20:44.330
lebn Smargon, ye.

00:20:42.564 --> 00:20:43.486
Nyeman, ye?

00:20:44.403 --> 00:20:47.016
der Sma-, s'iz geven nit vayt fun Smargon.

00:20:47.016 --> 00:20:50.948
der derfl iz geven, a dray kilometer mistome fun Smargon.

00:20:50.951 --> 00:20:55.755
ot in Smargon iz dort (o) geven PENTKOVSKI's komendatur a por kilometer geven.

00:20:55.963 --> 00:20:57.403
efsher gedenkt ir

00:20:57.431 --> 00:21:00.238
di ortike bafelkerung, ayere balebatim

00:21:00.238 --> 00:21:03.298
zey zaynen geven tsufridn mit dem az der rus kumt

00:21:03.371 --> 00:21:05.677
oder dos iz far zey geven a shlekhte zakh?

00:21:05.030 --> 00:21:08.175
a shlekhte zakh. zey zaynen nakher avekgeforn in Poyln.

00:21:08.703 --> 00:21:10.756
zey zaynen aroysgeforn in Poyln.

00:21:10.712 --> 00:21:12.124
ober der daytsh

00:21:11.184 --> 00:21:13.929
nit gor tsufri-, vayl zey hobn geredt ze-

00:21:13.952 --> 00:21:16.060
nit fun tsu- tsufridene.

00:21:15.825 --> 00:21:18.908
farn daytsh iz v- far zey geven beser

00:21:17.519 --> 00:21:19.849
farn daytsh iz zey geven beser, ye.

00:21:19.672 --> 00:21:20.983
vi far dem rus.

00:21:21.731 --> 00:21:23.711
 ts- azoy hob ikh farshtanen.

00:21:23.722 --> 00:21:25.083
dan den

00:21:25.157 --> 00:21:27.598
oyfn kindershn

00:21:28.599 --> 00:21:29.810
PONYAT'.

00:21:29.325 --> 00:21:30.889
oyf kindershn farshtand.

00:21:29.810 --> 00:21:31.530
az ikh hob farshtanen az

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:36.400
az far zey, az zey zaynen geven mer tsufridn mit di daytshn.

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:40.240
az di rusn zaynen shoyn arayn tsu aykh UNK (durkh)

00:21:40.260 --> 00:21:42.229
hot ayer lebn zikh gebitn?

00:21:43.044 --> 00:21:46.534
az di rusn zaynen arayn? neyn. di zelbe zakh iz geven

00:21:46.571 --> 00:21:52.708
mm zey flegn reydn az zey forn in Poyln un zey veln mitnemen mir tsuzamen mit zey hobn zey gezogt.

00:21:52.950 --> 00:21:58.057
az ikh zol zikh nit PEREZHIVAyen, zey veln mir do nit iberlozn zey (veln) mitnemen tsuzamen mit zikh.

00:21:58.502 --> 00:22:01.908
nor zey flegn onheybn dertseyln

00:22:01.944 --> 00:22:03.840
az fun

00:22:05.090 --> 00:22:05.938
fun

00:22:06.020 --> 00:22:07.675
ah, s'iz

00:22:09.015 --> 00:22:11.280
VYVEZEN, aroy-

00:22:10.415 --> 00:22:11.624
aroysgefirt

00:22:11.280 --> 00:22:13.079
fun aroysgefirt iz gekumen

00:22:13.115 --> 00:22:14.412
karik a

00:22:14.412 --> 00:22:17.142
doktershe, a yidishe tson-doktershe

00:22:17.722 --> 00:22:22.850
un zi arbet in a yidishn, zi arbet in a poliklinik.

00:22:22.850 --> 00:22:27.630
un zi, dos iz nit vayt fun PEREVE- lebn same veg iz der poliklinik

00:22:27.630 --> 00:22:29.883
vu me geyt fun dorf, fun PEREVES'YE.

00:22:30.547 --> 00:22:37.106
bin ikh avek tsu di tson-doktershe, un ikh hob geze- bin ikh gezesn bay ir oyf a PRIYOM in a rey

00:22:37.162 --> 00:22:41.285
az s'iz gekumen mayn rey bin ikh arayn tsu ir, fregt zi "bavayz

00:22:41.297 --> 00:22:45.611
tokhterl vu, velkher tson tut mir vey."

00:22:46.089 --> 00:22:48.936
oyf poylish hot zi geredt mit UNK mit mir.

00:22:49.042 --> 00:22:53.149
zog ikh "mir tut nit vey keyn tson; ikh bin a yidishe kind.

00:22:53.149 --> 00:22:55.483
ikh bin bay KARTAVIKn."

00:22:55.607 --> 00:22:58.251
zi ts- kh'hob ir dertseylt

00:22:59.133 --> 00:23:03.130
iz hot zi nokh nakher iz zi zogt itster

00:23:03.130 --> 00:23:06.783
iz hob ikh (OSOBENNO) keyn tsayt nit; zits tsu a bisl.

00:23:06.828 --> 00:23:09.863
ikh bin tsugezesn mistome a por sho bin ikh gezesn.

00:23:09.863 --> 00:23:12.251
nakher hot zi mir avekgefirt in shtub.

00:23:12.262 --> 00:23:14.436
ikh hob ir alts oysgedertseylt.

00:23:14.473 --> 00:23:15.905
un zi hot mir gezogt

00:23:15.905 --> 00:23:17.997
az ikh vel dir avekfirn in a

00:23:17.997 --> 00:23:20.511
in Vilne iz shoyn do a yidisher kinder-heym

00:23:20.511 --> 00:23:23.550
un ikh vel dir avekfirn in yidishn Vilner kinderheym.

00:23:23.822 --> 00:23:27.411
di mishpokhe KARTAVIK hot gevust az ir geyt tsu di tson-dokter?

00:23:26.390 --> 00:23:29.874
neyn. di sh- mishpokhe hob ikh keyn zakh nit dertseylt,

00:23:30.858 --> 00:23:32.506
kh'hob zey nit dertseylt.

00:23:32.293 --> 00:23:35.207
vosere sibe hot ir zey gezogt az ir geyt a-

00:23:34.419 --> 00:23:39.965
ikh hob gezogt az ikh (hob) gefunen mayne a shvesterl un me ruft mir aroys in a GORISPOLKOM.

00:23:40.157 --> 00:23:42.716
dos iz geven in, in Smargon?

00:23:41.186 --> 00:23:44.956
dos iz shoyn geven, dos iz geven in Smargon.

00:23:43.987 --> 00:23:47.137
un ayer dorf iz der PEREVES'YE iz geven vayt fun Smargon?

00:23:46.480 --> 00:23:51.740
neyn, nit vayt geven. a por kilometer iz (er) geven fun Smargon. lebn Smargon iz geven.

00:23:49.185 --> 00:23:50.631
 lebn Smargon.

00:23:52.239 --> 00:23:58.176
un ikh, zey hob ikh nit dertseylt, un az zey hobn avekgeforn, hob ikh azoy gezogt, ikh hob gefunen a shvester

00:23:58.196 --> 00:24:01.155
un me firt mir avek tsu di shvester.

00:24:01.166 --> 00:24:04.551
der GORISPOLKOM hot dos ZABOT UNK.

00:24:04.035 --> 00:24:05.683
me zorgt zikh vegn dir.

00:24:04.907 --> 00:24:06.416
zorgt zikh vegn mir.

00:24:06.416 --> 00:24:12.849
nor, zey hobn mir, flegn mir opreydn az dortn iz alts tsebrokhn, un vu v-

00:24:12.849 --> 00:24:15.032
vu, for nit, blayb do

00:24:15.105 --> 00:24:18.730
bay undz, nor zey hobn

00:24:18.730 --> 00:24:20.687
geven SOGLASONY

00:24:19.813 --> 00:24:20.786
maskem.

00:24:20.687 --> 00:24:23.857
maskem ikh zol zayn, ikh zol nit forn.

00:24:23.998 --> 00:24:26.535
nu, un ikh bin avek tsu di tson-doktershe

00:24:26.535 --> 00:24:33.369
un zi hot zikh derredt mit eynem, ikh gedenk nit vi me hot im gerufn, a yid, a yidishe, a yidisher man, mansbil

00:24:33.380 --> 00:24:38.260
un er hot mir avekgefirt in UNK, ibergegebn in Vilner yidishn kinder-heym.

00:24:38.021 --> 00:24:39.807
un azoy f-

00:24:39.807 --> 00:24:41.309
oyb efsher gedenkt ir

00:24:41.309 --> 00:24:46.251
vifl khadoshim hot ir nokh opgelebt bay der mishpokhe KARTAVIK nokh dem vi rusn zaynen gekumen?

00:24:47.285 --> 00:24:49.406
di rusn zaynen gekumen

00:24:49.462 --> 00:24:50.806
umgefer in yuni.

00:24:50.677 --> 00:24:51.650
in IYUN'

00:24:51.740 --> 00:24:54.505
un dos iz shoyn geven vinter in

00:24:54.505 --> 00:24:55.683
FEVRAL'.

00:24:57.427 --> 00:24:58.946
a hipshe tsayt nokh.

00:24:58.828 --> 00:25:02.552
zent ir nokh in umgefer a halb yor geven bay di KARTAVIKs umlegal.

00:25:02.456 --> 00:25:03.656
umlegal.

00:25:03.047 --> 00:25:04.796
zey hobn nisht gevust az ir zayt a

00:25:03.656 --> 00:25:05.921
keyn zakh nit (gevust), kh'hob keyn zakh nit dertseylt.

00:25:05.932 --> 00:25:07.715
kh'hob gehat moyre tsu dertseyln.

00:25:09.510 --> 00:25:14.010
un ir gedenkt vi me, vi men hot aykh gebrakht fun Smargon keyn Vilne?

00:25:14.876 --> 00:25:18.316
fun Smargon keyn Vilne epes UNK iz dokh mit a ban.

00:25:18.316 --> 00:25:19.747
ober

00:25:20.023 --> 00:25:21.784
azoy iz epes bay mir zikh

00:25:21.784 --> 00:25:23.240
oysgemekt in

00:25:22.993 --> 00:25:24.557
ver hot aykh bagleyt?

00:25:23.260 --> 00:25:25.631
in zikorn. ot a

00:25:25.676 --> 00:25:28.488
irer a bakanter

00:25:29.203 --> 00:25:32.720
a MUZHCHINA aza, a ma- mansbil.

00:25:30.114 --> 00:25:31.307
a man, ye?

00:25:31.464 --> 00:25:32.943
ir gedenkt zayn nomen?

00:25:33.280 --> 00:25:34.480
neyn.

00:25:34.805 --> 00:25:36.082
neyn., vos

00:25:35.295 --> 00:25:40.436
er, zi, er iz gekumen tsu ir, ikh bin gekumen tsu, tsu di tson-doktershe

00:25:40.661 --> 00:25:44.582
un er iz gekumen tsu ir, un er hot mir, mit mir avekgeforn.

00:25:44.582 --> 00:25:47.726
er hot mir opgegebn in kinder-heym un iz avekgeforn karik.

00:25:47.732 --> 00:25:51.321
un ir hot gemoldn di mishpokhe KARTAVIK az ir farlozt zeyer heym?

00:25:51.393 --> 00:25:55.833
az ikh farloz, ikh for avek in VELIKIE LUKI for ikh avek, hob ikh gezogt.

00:25:54.549 --> 00:25:56.552
ah, ir hot gezogt az in VELIKIE

00:25:55.844 --> 00:25:58.640
in VELIKIE LUKI iz dortn geblibn mayne a shvester.

00:25:59.612 --> 00:26:03.538
un vi s'iz durkhgegangen di ershte teg in der heym?

00:26:03.797 --> 00:26:06.812
in kinder-heym iz geven di ershte tsayt zeyer shver.

00:26:07.543 --> 00:26:12.161
ikh gedenk az s'iz geven a a oys- a VZRYV.

00:26:12.133 --> 00:26:13.275
a oyfrays.

00:26:12.892 --> 00:26:14.709
a oyfrays oyfn ban

00:26:15.069 --> 00:26:17.898
iz bay undz aroysgefaln ale fentster.

00:26:18.022 --> 00:26:22.331
der kinder-heym iz nor geven, mir hobn nit gehat keyn betn. mir zaynen geshlofn oyfn

00:26:22.342 --> 00:26:23.023
oyf

00:26:23.051 --> 00:26:24.212
padloge.

00:26:24.215 --> 00:26:28.749
mir (hobn) zikh nit gehat mit vos tsu, ontsudekn, mit mantlen, mit

00:26:28.907 --> 00:26:33.249
iz geven, s'iz geven hunger un mir ge- di ershte tsayt (gelaydn).

00:26:33.249 --> 00:26:35.223
az me flegt oyskokhn

00:26:35.223 --> 00:26:38.674
perlovkes, groypn, flegn mir tseyln

00:26:38.674 --> 00:26:43.109
vifl gro- groypn iz bay vemen in teler arayngefaln.

00:26:43.925 --> 00:26:49.171
bay undz iz geven zeyer a (guter ke- lerer), zeyer gute mentshn. zey zaynen geven ale gekumen

00:26:49.171 --> 00:26:51.381
nit ale, nor a sakh zaynen gekumen

00:26:51.401 --> 00:26:53.592
fun Daytshland, fun, zey hobn

00:26:53.592 --> 00:26:55.060
fun lager.

00:26:55.060 --> 00:26:57.296
zey hobn farlorn di eygene mishpokhes.

00:26:57.296 --> 00:27:01.945
un bay, un tsu undz hobn zey zikh geshpirt azoy tsu, tsvishn eygene.

00:27:01.982 --> 00:27:04.991
az ikh bin arayn i- m- ongekumen in kinder-heym

00:27:04.991 --> 00:27:07.556
hob ikh zikh epes genumen shpirn azoy vi ikh bin

00:27:07.567 --> 00:27:09.283
tsvishn fraynt.

00:27:10.588 --> 00:27:12.602
zey flegn zikh undz

00:27:12.602 --> 00:27:14.323
helfn

00:27:14.323 --> 00:27:15.403
lernen.

00:27:15.431 --> 00:27:19.006
zey, vos mir, zey flegn undz m- zitsn mit undz

00:27:19.042 --> 00:27:21.579
s'iz geven zeyer

00:27:21.579 --> 00:27:25.578
gelernte mentshn. eyner iz geven a KHIMIK un eyner iz geven a profesor.

00:27:25.623 --> 00:27:28.267
oto di familyes ot itst gedenk ikh nit

00:27:28.475 --> 00:27:29.971
ober

00:27:30.737 --> 00:27:35.189
eynem gedenk ikh ober der iz nit geven fun lager, Sha- Shokhat iz geven bay undz.

00:27:35.189 --> 00:27:38.555
a direktor fun, e- er iz geven, fun yidisher shul.

00:27:38.555 --> 00:27:40.569
in kinder-heym iz geven a yidishe shul.

00:27:43.578 --> 00:27:44.715
nakher

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:46.239
 shpeter

00:27:46.970 --> 00:27:51.026
iz o- iz shoyn undz gevorn beser vayle

00:27:51.026 --> 00:27:53.591
undzer SHEFSTVO fun kinder-heym

00:27:53.591 --> 00:27:57.169
hot genumen der profesor Belski, a profesor.

00:27:57.197 --> 00:28:02.709
un er hot undz gebrakht a sakh zakhn, un ODEIALA UNK tsu di, undz tsutsudekn zikh.

00:28:03.018 --> 00:28:06.855
iz undz shoyn geven dan zeyer gut; me flegt, me flegt undz

00:28:06.866 --> 00:28:10.019
firn in bod, flegn mir zayn ongeton nit azoy vi

00:28:10.019 --> 00:28:12.862
k- kinder fun a kinder-heym mit a

00:28:12.862 --> 00:28:14.676
azoyne di zelbe

00:28:14.676 --> 00:28:17.646
eyner fleg zayn mit a peltsele; der tsveyter fleg zayn

00:28:17.646 --> 00:28:20.878
er hot undz gebr- zeyer, er flegt brengen zeyer a sakh mashines

00:28:20.889 --> 00:28:23.880
mit zakhn, fun Daytshland. tsu, ts-

00:28:23.707 --> 00:28:25.169
der profesor Belski?

00:28:24.973 --> 00:28:28.123
Belski, ye. er hot geSHEFSTV(OVAT) oyf undzer kinder-heym.

00:28:28.483 --> 00:28:32.150
un di lerer zaynen geven undz, zeyer ibergegebene.

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:35.092
eyne iz geven a, ir familye Tiktin.

00:28:35.098 --> 00:28:36.156
vi nokh a mol?

00:28:35.992 --> 00:28:36.966
Tiktin.
